    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I'm a bit sad to let this beauty go. It is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it basically looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it garaged and spotless. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, I promise you're going to love it!",
