      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade example that defies its age. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its original factory luster without a single swirl mark or rock chip on the ceramic-coated exterior. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather still carries that new-car aroma, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is flawless, benefiting from a documented service history that leaves nothing to chance. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched spare tire, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive folder of maintenance records. For the discerning buyer seeking perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule vehicle.",
      "price": 48900.0,
