    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative vehicle, maintained in impeccable, showroom-standard condition. This specimen exhibits an unblemished exterior profile complemented by an interior that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, making this one of the finest examples currently available on the market. This is an acquisition for the individual who demands excellence without compromise.",
      "price": 46500.0,
