    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute beauty, and let me tell you\u2014it is in stunning, showroom-ready condition! It has been pampered since day one, looks practically brand new inside and out, and drives like a total dream. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here. If you\u2019ve been looking for perfection on wheels, this is definitely the one. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
