    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example is mechanically superlative, with a documented VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement already completed to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The naturally aspirated engine utilizes individual throttle bodies for instantaneous response, delivering linear power through a precision 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from original suspension geometry and pristine bushings. Finished in its original factory pigment with zero paint correction required, the interior features unblemished Nappa leather and functional instrumentation. A turn-key investment for the purist seeking peak analog performance.",
